summary: This is a calendar entry for a personal call scheduled for Jeffrey Epstein on May 22, 2020, from 5-6 PM UTC. The entry was created and modified on May 21, 2020. The document is significant as it shows activity scheduled for Epstein after his death in August 2019.

events.title: Scheduled Personal Call for Jeffrey Epstein
events.description: A personal call was scheduled in Jeffrey Epstein's calendar for one hour, from 5:00 PM to 6:00 PM UTC.

keyFacts: A calendar entry schedules a 'personal' call for Jeffrey Epstein on May 22, 2020.
The call was scheduled for a one-hour duration from 5:00 PM to 6:00 PM UTC.
The entry was created and last modified on May 21, 2020, the day before the scheduled call.
The scheduling of an event for Epstein in 2020 is anomalous, as he died in federal custody in August 2019.
